title: Dudley cinema screening Ed Sheeran's latest film
text:
Filmed during his X Tour across three sold-out nights at Wembley Stadium in front of 240,000 fans, Jumpers for Goalposts includes an additional 90 minutes of concert footage. 
Tickets for the screening are available to book from the Odeon website at www.odeon.co.uk/films Receive daily email updates from the Express & Star
